\title{Kleene equality}
\meta{external}{https://ncatlab.org/nlab/show/Kleene+equality}
\taxon{definition}

\p{In the context of [partial functions](math-0057) where we can have undefined values, \em{Kleene equality} is defined as:}

#{a \rightleftharpoons b := (a = b \text{ if both defined}) \vee \text{ both undefined} }

\p{\em{Directed} Kleene equality is defined as:}
#{a \overline{\leftharpoondown} b := (a = b \text{ if both defined}) \vee a \text{ undefined}}